profile_positions.description:
- Implementation of guidelines on the prevention of child maltreatment; 
- Supporting doctors and nurses at GGD Twente, and child maltreatment officers, in dealing with suspicions of child maltreatment, by organizing training and peer supervision, and writing internal guidelines;
- Improving cooperation between GGD Twente and other organizations involved in tackling child abuse;
- Project leader two-year project "Supporting child abuse experts in Twente".
